      "content": "but that feels like such a bandaid solution, you know? like putting a tiny sticker on a gaping wound. all those efforts... they're just delaying the inevitable. it feels so much more honest to just admit that it's over. it's exhausting to keep pretending that things are actually going to change when the data says otherwise.",
